{
  "texts": [
    "The provided image is converted to grayscale and de-noised using Gaussian blur for image processing.",
    "After that, Otsu's technique and adaptive Gaussian thresholding altered the grayscale image.",
    "Form-based morphological procedures were then performed on the image.",
    "They also proposed a novel algorithm and image-processing approach.",
    "Texture features are retrieved utilizing statistical parameters and GLCM, which are applied to extract features from the segmented images with enhanced quality."
  ]
}